{"tid":2103140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次初選係第一次亦係最後一次，一定要投本土！","createTime":"2020-07-11T04:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T13:56:20.000Z","uid":234894,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8c0bddd0dce972f2bdb2f7857547dbf1301c41","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"今次初選，好多自稱素人同埋抗爭者嘅候選人，搞到好多真正本土嘅手足被忽略。如果本土候選人嘅票數大大拋離泛民，就可以證明香港嘅主流民意就係要本土，本土嘅聲音先可以被全世界聽到，脫離泛民嘅魔爪。請大家all in 王伯（又名超區坦克車）同埋張可森（新西）。其他區就有本土投本土。"},{"pid":"a3477ac7f38c6311385d9cb0813ca6f2f007181e","tid":2103140,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"44d07d47a854a4f4a6f5ec0e7f323428358c49a6","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37d42d9ac3e4d74ea7e020080e22f4b5e6e09ad3","tid":2103140,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14961959d46f41cd4be351c275d43a23161f1fea","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a175080537575f128d430dcf10a26ffc82affb8c","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"d675a1a429347904d143738ba9f66b9881be9866","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebffbfceba3ec5c94bc39e65fc2862cb8bcf73e9","tid":2103140,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"968190355291947cf79f018b9a5a03d85ebdfb11","tid":2103140,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},